function.arg:
<%@ livebos language='javascript' %>
var fhbz = ABS_SQLVALUE("select paramvalue from jgcrm.tsysparam  where paramname='ams.system'");
var fhz=true;
if(fhbz==0){
  fhz=true;
}else{
  var bean = ABS_LOADBEAN("com.apex.bss.mod.ibb.systemdocking.apexsoft.livebosbean.TaskEndBean");

  var note = result.get('O_NOTE');
  if(code > 0){
      ABS_SETRETNOTE(note);
     fhz= true;
   }else{
      ABS_SETRETNOTE(note);
      fhz= false;
   }
}
fhz;

condition.name: abs.FormExpOfStepCondition
condition.arg:
<%@ livebos language='javascript' %>
var sfhb = O_WORKFLOW.SFHB;
var sfnk = ABS_SQLVALUE("SELECT count(1)  FROM ECIF.LCIB_GS_LXLC_BJMX WHERE LCIB_GS_LXLC_ID = ? and BJR = ? and SFNKRY = 1",[O_WORKFLOW.ID,$Login.User]);

   c3 = ABS_SQLVALUE("SELECT CEIL( COUNT(1)*1/3 ) FROM ECIF.LCIB_GS_LXLC_BJMX WHERE LCIB_GS_LXLC_ID = ? AND BJYJ IS NOT NULL  AND BJYJ <> 5 ",[O_WORKFLOW.ID]);
}
var c4;

   c4 = ABS_SQLVALUE("SELECT COUNT(1)+1 FROM ECIF.LCIB_GS_LXLC_BJMX WHERE LCIB_GS_LXLC_ID = ? AND BJYJ IS NOT NULL and  BJYJ <> 5 and SFNKRY = 1",[O_WORKFLOW.ID]);
}else{
   c4 = ABS_SQLVALUE("SELECT COUNT(1)  FROM ECIF.LCIB_GS_LXLC_BJMX WHERE LCIB_GS_LXLC_ID = ? AND BJYJ IS NOT NULL and  BJYJ <> 5 and SFNKRY = 1",[O_WORKFLOW.ID]);
}
